dct_description_sm: ex officina Judoci Hondii ; D Grijp sculpt.
North oriented toward right of sheet.
Decorative border and cartouches, compass rose, royal coat of arms.
Shows topography, vegetation, waterways, Native American villages.
Inset illustration: Status regis Powhatan quando prefectus Smith Captivus.
